**Date/Time**&nbsp;  
Date(s) - 08/14/2021&nbsp;  
6:30 am - 1:30 pm&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  

**Location**&nbsp;  
[Forest Park Golf Course](https://goo.gl/maps/ucdV6grqGNA7zaKS9)&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  

Mark your calendars and get signed up for this year's Bomber Open on August 14th, at Forest Park Golf Course.
Last year we** SOLD OUT** at 144 golfers for both courses, this year we want to take over all three courses at Forest Park but the only way to do so is to have 180 golfers signed up by July 31st.
&nbsp;  

If you sign up and pay by July 31st you have a chance to win a **4K LED TV in the Early Bird Raffle**!
This is the clubs biggest fund raising event and one of the most entertaining events as well.
Registration is at 6:30AM with a shotgun start at 7:30AM. There will be some snacks and a breakfast sandwich at the morning bar, but would recommend having breakfast before arriving.  
&nbsp;  

Price is **$130** per golfer, **$520 for 4-some**. Prices go up to **$150-$600** respectively if you pay day of event.
We have multiple sponsor levels including the Gift Sponsor which includes your logo on all the gifts the golfers will receive on the day of the event. Contact Neal Ford at [events@stlouisbombers.com](mailto:events@stlouisbombers.com). 
&nbsp;  

There will beverages served throughout the course with multiple game holes and raffles. Lunch will follow with awards and a Silent Auction throughout the day as well. Check out our wish list to where you can donate an item to the Silent Auction through our [Amazon Wish List (https://www.stlouisbombers.com/wish-list). 
&nbsp;  

Get signed up and registered today!  
&nbsp;  

Sign Up: [https://www.stlouisbombers.com/golf](https://www.stlouisbombers.com/golf). 
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  

[More Info](https://www.stlouisbombers.com/events/2021-st-louis-bombers-open/?fbclid=IwAR39L2Hwdi3SokUsnpzjYAs86A7FaKLpx6mGzz2VuXPcgfCO-WlPikawgTU)
